fields.title: Ribs
fields.description: Traditional dish infused with robust flavours

fields.title: noodle
fields.description: Fried noodles filled with meats and vegetables.  It is a great comfort dish to share with family and friends.

fields.title: nachos
fields.description: Nachos are a favorite dish for after evening affairs.  Great to enjoy with groups of friends.

fields.title: korean
fields.description: Korean short raised ribs.  This is a super powerful experience that excites the senses and invokes the exotic.

fields.title: haupia
fields.description: Classic Hawaiian dish made with coconut and other natural ingredients.

fields.title: Jambon starter
fields.description: A classic starter with prosciutto ham.  Very tasty.

fields.title: Spring Rolls
fields.description: Vietnamese style spring rolls.  Made with lots of fresh crab (chunked meat) and fresh herbs and vegetables.  Made for sharing.

fields.title: Lobster
fields.description: Lobster made with gourmet level enhancements.   Flavour profile is professional and requires wine and other white tablecloth attention.
